  <Category>Tools:System</Category>
  <Name>Unraid AI CLI Agents</Name>
  <Description>Integrated AICliAgents CLI for AI-assisted Unraid server management.</Description>
  <Overview>
    Unraid AICliAgents CLI brings the power of AICli's AI-assisted management directly to your Unraid WebUI.
    
    [b]Features:[/b]
    - AI-assisted server management.
    - Integrated CLI interface.
    - Human-in-the-Loop (HITL) safety for critical operations.
  </Overview>
  <Support>https://forums.unraid.net/topic/197460-plugin-support-unraid-tab-for-ai-cli-coding-agents-gemini-cli-claude-code-opencode-kilo-code-pi-coder-codex-cli-factory-droid-cli-copilot-nano-coder/</Support>
